 # Pre-Commit Quality Checks

```yaml
name: Pre-Commit Quality Checks
description: Runs quality checks similar to GitHub Actions locally before commits
author: Cursor AI
version: 1.0.0
tags:
  - quality
  - pre-commit
  - testing
